name: effeffIX Concept Diffusion
description:
Fine-tuned Stable Diffusion model, based off F222, trained with concept art from a high quality role playing game.

This model was trained on multiple concepts which can be used as tokens in your prompts.

Use the token effeff9 combined with:

  • woman

  • man

  • creature

  • architecture

Example prompt:

Wide shot of a effeff9 woman warrior aubrey plaza with shining armor descending from heaven, lifelike, (highly detailed eyes), super highly detailed face, professional digital painting, artstation, concept art, Unreal Engine 5, HD quality, 8k resolution, beautiful, cinematic, art by artgerm and greg rutkowski and alphonse mucha and loish and WLOP


Steps: 82, Sampler: DPM++ 2M, CFG scale: 8.5, Seed: 695884347, Size: 512x512, Model hash: b7ba5b22

Negative prompt template: https://huggingface.co/zuleo/effeffIX-concept-diffusion#%E2%9D%8E-negative-prompt-template

🧾 More Prompt examples: https://huggingface.co/zuleo/effeffIX-concept-diffusion
